REACTION   (26-FE-0(G,ABS),,SIG,,BRS)
COMMENT    Because the Fe-56 isotope abundance is 91.7 % the
            measured cross section can be examined as
            26-Fe-56(gamma,abs).
           The nuclear absorption cross section was obtsained by
            subtrsacting from the experimrental curve the
            theoretical atomic absorption cross section.
